      "title": "The train coming to Colombo stops",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Railway General Manager Dhammika Jayasundara said that due to the imposition of curfew in Colombo district, all trains scheduled to run from the outer provinces to Colombo were suspended and the trains scheduled to leave Colombo this afternoon will run as normal."
